headline: 3 Big Reasons to Love Monster (MNST)
summary: Even during a down period for the markets, Monster has gone against the grain, climbing to $58.33. Its shares have yielded a 13.7% return over the last six months, beating the S&P 500 by 23.6%. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
